Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now add these Southern spices into the mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:28.31,Penguin_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,では　この南蛮ドライの粉末を入れてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll melt into sludge!
